
setup / building:
1. must have java, java-devel
2. `make libs` to download dependencies
3. `make build-jar` to build jar

native:
1. `make run-jar` to run jar (or `java -jar lingua-api.jar`)

docker / podman:

1. create images:
    `make podman-image`
    `make docker-image`
2. run images:
    [podman/docker] run -it --net=host -e LINGUA_API_PORT=80 --name lingua-api lingua-api  
